<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Closes Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, April 10 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at Tehran
Stock Exchange on Saturday closed at 1555.86 points, up 4.36
points from Wednesday' finish.
</P>
