cooperation and investment between east and west China which began
Tuesday. Shaanxi has offered some 70 tourism investment projects
involving seven billion yuan (843 million U.S. dollars) for
investors at the event.
</P>
<P>
Some 16 projects involving a total investment of 200 million
yuan were signed in the first three days alone. These projects are
related to resource development, highway construction, cable-way
equipment and the construction of recreational centers. The fair
also yielded contracts for tourism handicrafts valued at over 200
million yuan.
</P>
