<HEADLINE> Gold Price in Hong Kong Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, April 10 (Xinhua) -- The gold price in Hong Kong
dropped 197 HK dollars to close at 2,603 HK dollars a tael on
Saturday, according to Po Sang Bank, one of the major gold dealers
in Hong Kong.
</P>
<P>
The gold price is equivalent to 282.02 U.S. dollars a troy
ounce, or 21.31 U.S. dollars down from the previous close at
Saturday's exchange rate of one U.S. dollar against 7.7475 HK
dollars. 
</P>
</TEXT>
