<HEADLINE> Albania Says to Recognize "Kosovo Government" </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TIRANA, April 9 (Xinhua) -- Albania will recognize the "Kosovo
government" established by the Kosovo Liberation Army (KLA) early
this month, said Albanian Prime Minister Pandeli Majko on Friday.
</P>
<P>
The self-claimed government, which consists of members of the
KLA and the Kosovo Democratic United Front seeking separation of
the province from the Republic of Serbia, Yugoslavia, has not won
any international recognition.
</P>
