<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, April 9 (Xinhua) -- Chelsea skipper, Dennis Wise, could
face a UEFA investigation after video footage from Thursday's Cup
Winners' Cup clash appeared to show him attempting to bite Real
Mallorca's Elena Marcelino.
</P>
<P>
Wise, who has already been sent off three times this season,
apparently reacted to provocation from Marcelino. But his actions
may prompt UEFA to launch an investigation into the incident.
</P>
