coach Ray Wilkins has vowed to examine TV replays.
</P>
<P>
Wilkins said: "I can't honestly say I saw that while the game
was going on.
</P>
<P>
"We will have to see the replay and see what the situation is."
</P>
<P>
Marcelino, who may have been guilty of digging his fingernails
into Wise's neck, said: "He caught me with his hand and tried to
provoke me.
</P>
<P>
"I had to be very calm but someone has told me that he also
tried to bite me. It is certainly not common but I didn't feel
anything.
</P>
<P>
"The referee also didn't see anything so he is very clever.
He's a good player but has a strong character and maybe that's his
problem," he said. 
